  "name": "Attack Roll Modifiers",
  "content": "<p>See @Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.Q8vJfOFojro5BrWO]{2.06. Combat Modifiers}</p>\n<table class=\"inner\" style=\"height: 211px; width: 396px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 230px; height: 16px;\"><strong>Attacker is...</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 71px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\"><strong>Melee</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 93px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\"><strong>Ranged</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 230px; height: 16px;\">Dazzled</td>\n<td style=\"width: 71px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 93px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 19px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 230px; height: 19px;\">Entangled</td>\n<td style=\"width: 71px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">-2<sup>1</sup></td>\n<td style=\"width: 93px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">-2<sup>1</sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 230px; height: 16px;\">Flanking defender</td>\n<td style=\"width: 71px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 93px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 19px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 230px; height: 19px;\">Invisible</td>\n<td style=\"width: 71px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">+2<sup>2</sup></td>\n<td style=\"width: 93px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">+2<sup>2</sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 230px; height: 16px;\">On higher ground</td>\n<td style=\"width: 71px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 93px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 19px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 230px; height: 19px;\">Prone</td>\n<td style=\"width: 71px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">-4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 93px; height: 19px; text-align: center;\">&mdash;<sup>3</sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 230px; height: 16px;\">Shaken or frightened</td>\n<td style=\"width: 71px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 93px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 230px; height: 16px;\">Squeezing through a space</td>\n<td style=\"width: 71px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 93px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-4</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>1 An entangled character also takes a &ndash;4 penalty to Dexterity, which may affect his attack roll.<br />2 The defender loses any Dexterity bonus to AC.<br />3 Most ranged weapons can&rsquo;t be used while the attacker is prone, but you can use a crossbow or shuriken while prone at no penalty.</p>",
